{"tid":2380680,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"藥房大王兩億搶舖變輸家｜ 水貨客絕跡 龍豐貴舖賣平價零食 「洗底」死頂","createTime":"2021-01-26T05:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T05:24:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"507e2e4a653ebd94f89e0c986bc44d3659f3322c","tid":2380680,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"藥房大王兩億搶舖變輸家｜<br />\n水貨客絕跡 龍豐貴舖賣平價零食 「洗底」死頂 <br />\n#財經－壹週刊 Next <br />\n原刊日期：20210113<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3e4QSUNUxgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3e4QSUNUxgc&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=d09221d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3e4QSUNUxgc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊 NEXT<br />\n698K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n曾被揭發賣假藥的龍豐藥房，多年來在自由行力撐下生意火紅，分店由上水開到尖沙咀達22間。身兼黑龍江政協的老闆謝少海，被冠以「藥房大王」之稱。同時他又覷準時機炒樓炒舖，豬籠入水，身家暴漲至逾八億，幾年前雄心壯志道：「我哋目標開50間分店！」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/i20OUyIn0cb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2Fi20OUyIn0cb&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=98d4017c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/i20OUyIn0cb</a><br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"7a14fb1a4ee8931c2a006aad4481bd22a744de9a","tid":2380680,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"龍豐呢啲明顯賤人"}]}